snippet.title: The Lord of the Rings: Return to Moria™ - Launch Trailer (15s Version)
snippet.description:
The Lord of the Rings: Return to Moria, the only survival crafting game set in the Fourth Age of Middle-earth™, the iconic fantasy world created by J.R.R. Tolkien. 

Available now on PC via the Epic Games Store. PlayStation 5 digitally via the PlayStation Store and physically at retail from 5th of Dec. Xbox Series X|S coming early 2024 (exact date TBD)

Buy now on Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/the-lord-of-the-rings-return-to-moria-f01344
Wishlist on PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10008445/

Find out more at www.ReturnToMoria.com

Official Socials:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ReturnToMoria
Discord: https://discord.gg/6TNP7as9md
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@returntomoria
